vote.title: An ordinance abandoning portions of two utility easements to RB East Wing Property LLC and RB Land 2 LLC, the abutting owners, containing a total of approximately 36,861 square feet of land, located near the intersection of Camp Wisdom Road and Interstate Highway 67 - Revenue: General Fund $5,400.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
